rows.text: Adds the new Legendary Lord Wurrzag, who leads a new Greenskins sub-faction, The Bloody Handz.
Adds the new hero Grey Wizard to The Empire.
Adds the new hero Jade Wizard to The Empire.
Adds the new Legendary Lord Grombrindal to the Dwarfs. Grombrindal was previously available as part of a special promotion.
Updated the Bretonnia faction, made them a free playable race, along with two subfactions: Bordeleaux and Carcassonne.
Adds the Von Carstein faction, with Legendary Lord Isabella von Carstein. Migrates Vlad von Carstein to the Von Carstein faction.
Adds several Regiments of Renown to DLC and Free-LC races. This requires signing up for Total War Access.
